  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0ba8\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bc8 \u0b9a\u0bc0\u0ba9\u0bbe \u0b95\u0bcc\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bae\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b95\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0ba4\u0bc1 - \u0ba4\u0bc2\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc0 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb9\u0bca\u0b99\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "China considers donation to Sri Lanka as an honor - Ambassador Kei Senhong",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The 5,000 metric tons of rice donated by China will be used to feed students in all nine provinces. In response, the Minister of Education told the Chinese Ambassador to Sri Lanka that the Chinese government was welcome to co-operate with China in the face of the crisis.",
        "Sri Lankans are facing an economic crisis. We have decided to provide nutritious food to children from low income families who have been severely affected economically.",
        "Chinese Ambassador to Sri Lanka Kei Senhong said that China considers the donation as an honor.",
        "China has decided to donate 10,000 metric tons of rice to Sri Lanka on the occasion of the 70th anniversary of the signing of the Sri Lanka Rubber-Rice Agreement.",
        "Chinese Ambassador to Sri Lanka Ki-Senhong handed over 5,000 metric tons of rice to Education Minister Bandula Gunawardena yesterday.",
        "Commenting on this, Transport, Highways and Media Minister Bandula Gunawardena welcomed China's cooperation in the face of the worst economic crisis.",
        "The historic good relations between China and Sri Lanka have further strengthened the cooperation and good relations between the two countries.",
        "The 5,000 metric tons of rice available will be used to feed millions of students in 7,900 schools in 9 provinces. On behalf of Sri Lanka, I would like to thank the Chinese Government.",
        "Chinese Ambassador to Sri Lanka Xi Hong Kong, who attended on behalf of the Chinese Government, said China has co-operated with Sri Lanka on all occasions in the face of the crisis situation in Sri Lanka.",
        "Minister Bandula Gunawardena stated that all necessary assistance will be provided for the nutrition of the school children.",
        "China is honored to donate during an emergency. The surplus 5,000 metric tons of rice will be delivered soon.",
        "The Sri Lankan brothers are facing the current economic crisis. Most families in the total population face this problem.",
        "We decided to provide nutritious food to children from low-income families who have been severely affected economically. He said Sri Lankans would face the current crisis together and make rapid progress."
      ],
